 Note: This Group Policy path may not exist by default.

It is provided by the Group Policy template 'WindowsDefender.admx/adml' that is included with the Microsoft Windows 8.1 & Server 2012 R2 Administrative Templates (or newer).

 Impact:

 None - this is the default behavior."
